#keralawedding #keralaweddingstyles #keralahinduwedding #keralahindubridalmakeup #iyerbride #brahminbride #makeupartistinkerala #keralawesdingstories #makeupartistinkottayam

While am writing this, tears well up in my eyes, and I’m not sure why. I vividly remember our meeting in 2019, when we were both professionals in our respective fields……me as a makeup artist and u as a model. It was the beginning of my career, and you supported me unconditionally in every aspect. Your unwavering support has been beyond words, and I am immensely grateful for it. Despite having numerous other prominent contacts to choose  for your wedding makeup, u specifically chose me. I feel an overwhelming sense of joy and pride knowing that I will have the opportunity to work on ur special day.
 
Beyond our professional connection, I feel a deep emotional bond, as if I’m bidding farewell to my sister on her wedding day. Words cannot capture the depth of emotions I’m experiencing right now. It’s difficult to explain the significance of this relationship. I am overjoyed that you have found the perfect life partner. May you always be blessed, and I wholeheartedly wish you a lifetime of happiness in your married life.I was not able to attend ur wedding because of some work commitments but my mind was with u😭😭🥰
